  <brief_title>The Effect of an Inpatient Home-work Exercise Program on Leg Function After Stroke</brief_title>
  <official_title>Exercise Programs for Stroke: Effect of an Inpatient Supplementary Practice Program on Lower Extremity Function</official_title>
